{"tid":2349104,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟重推買斷版Office","createTime":"2021-01-01T09:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T10:40:17.000Z","uid":1086,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c4d78c72475ba15418a0c1f6076fbca043446c","tid":2349104,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2821182/shing3_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2821182%2Fshing3_1024.jpg&h=c7e51d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年來的科技企業營運趨勢都偏向訂閱制，每月用小量金錢訂閱服務，毋須一次過付大筆錢完全購買。最常見當然是Netflix（NFLX）、Adobe（ADBE）等服務。微軟（MSFT）亦有其Microsoft 365，提供訂閱版的Office軟件，但仍有不少人堅持買斷Office，最後一個買斷版Office為Office 2019，Office 2016甚至Office 2013仍有不少人使用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n舊版Office最大問題是相容性及更新問題，有朝一日微軟或停止支援舊版，如同它停止支援IE更新，令人擔心是否要屈服於訂閱制之下。<br />\n<br />\n但最近微軟官方表示，將於2021年下半年發布新版的買斷式Office軟件，可見官方沒有放棄買斷式軟件。新版Office將支援Windows及Mac OS作業系統。外界估計，新Office的程式與以往差不多，都有常用的Word、Excel、PowerPoint等，但一切細節還有待官方公布。"},{"pid":"4e0dacca1bd981b8c59a3c292f50df5bbe4b17af","tid":2349104,"uid":7854,"like":8,"dislike":31,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"淘寶$10就可以買斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866e5b1d1488eb74ab175b2c301754b821012976","tid":2349104,"uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"4e0dacca1bd981b8c59a3c292f50df5bbe4b17af","tid":2349104,"uid":7854,"like":8,"dislike":31,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T09:44:28.000Z","msg":"淘寶$10就可以買斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"libreoffice $0"},{"pid":"da656f50c4b3b82714bfec964fb0876add2e683c","tid":2349104,"uid":33874,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"自己整咗個教育版<br />\n唔好玩啦仲一個個月俾"},{"pid":"3e4695c3e7ca03df8474eae